55+ ACTIVE LIVING ON FLORIDA’S EAST COAST!
Situated on the East Coast of Florida, Palm Lake Club is an attractive, age-restricted mobile home community with a variety of activities to compliment all lifestyles.
Surrounded by beautiful lakes, beaches, and wildlife preserves, residents and vacationers alike have the choice of many area attractions to explore. Or stay at home and enjoy the community activities and lifestyle, which includes a sparkling in ground heated pool, a clubhouse, a fully stocked library, and so much more!
Palm Lake Club is home to friendly, caring and fun-loving residents. Beautiful landscaping and a huge 16-acre lake make this community a truly serene place to live. Whether you’re looking to relax or get active, Palm Lake Club is ready to serve you
